# UPMEM Swap - .gitignore
# Essential: src/, simulator/src/, scripts/*.py
# Ignore: build artifacts, logs, autogenerated docs, generated images

## Build & Compilation
build/
*.o
*.a
*.so
*.dylib
*.out
CMakeCache.txt
CMakeFiles/
cmake_install.cmake
Makefile

## Binaries
swap_sim
benchmark_*
test_*
dpu_tasklets
host

## IDE & Editors
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.DS_Store

## Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.egg-info/
.pytest_cache/

## Logs & Temporary Files
*.log
*.tmp
*.bak
*.orig
*.txt
*.tex
*.aux
*.toc
*.out
*.bbl
*.blg
*.jpg
*.png
*.pdf
*.csv

## Data & Results
results_*.csv
benchmark_results.csv
analysis_report.txt
simulator_dump.txt
simulator/results/*.log
simulator/results/*.csv

## Prototypes & WIP
Makefilemake
*.backup
*_old.*

## Misc
prompter.sh
project_context.txt
quick_install.sh.bak
